[Name] lm_sensors
[Summary] Linux sensors drivers and hardware monitoring tools.
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] lm_sensors provides essential drivers for monitoring the temperatures, voltages, and fans of Linux systems with hardware monitoring devices. It contains drivers for sensor chips and I2C and SMBus masters, text-based tools for sensor reporting, and a library for sensors access called 'libsensors'. It also contains tools for sensor hardware identification and I2C bus probing.
[Homepage] http://www2.lm-sensors.nu/~lm78/
